title: Ep. - 308 - EXECUTIVE PRODUCER OF THE CHALLENGE ON MTV ALYSSA AMOROSO
description:
Kate talks about We Are The Champions on Netflix, which documents six widely different and very unique competitions across the world.

 

Julie Pizzi serves as President of Entertainment and Development at Bunim/Murray Productions (BMP) and Executive Producer of The Challenge, a reality game show on MTV that is spun off from two of the network's reality shows, The Real World and Road Rules. Season 36, The Challenge: Double Agents, premieres on December 9.

 

Podcast host and Tik Tok star Alyssa Amoroso reviews the season finale of Keeping Up With the Kardashians.
